                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperator</rs> augustus. Noverit omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/188"
                            >Grimaldum</persName> gloriosum <rs key="#Emperor/king">comitem</rs> nec
                        non et <persName key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke #fidelisOf"
                            ref="#people/1502">Odelricum</persName> inclitum <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >marchionem</rs> dilectissimos <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideles nostros</rs>
                        humiliter nostram exorasse <rs key="#Intercessory">clementiam</rs>, quatenus
                        quandam <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property">iuris regi nostri</rs> quae <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Iudiciaria #Decima #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/1404"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ref="#places/1804">Girpa</placeName></geogName> nominatur simul cum
                            <rs key="#Churches">capella</rs> in honore <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1404">domini Salvatoris</orgName> consecrata
                        pertinentem videlicet de <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124"><placeName ref="#places/59"
                                >Veronensi</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus adiacentiis et
                        pertinentiis suis ex integro, sicut dudum de eodem comitatu pertinuit,
                            <persName key="#Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/165"
                            >Ingelfredo</persName> glorioso <rs key="#Count">comiti</rs> dilectoque
                            <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideli</rs> nostro iure proprietario concedere
                        dignaremur. Quorum precibus acclinati, prenominatam curtem Girpam simul cum
                        capella in honore domini Salvatoris constructa, sicut huc usque de comitatu
                        Veronensi pertinuit, cum omnibus adiacentiis et appendiciis suis suoque domo
                        cultili, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs> videlicet, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs>sacionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis
                            aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et
                            ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Profits_of_justice">districtionibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciariis</rs>, <rs key="#Decima">decimis</rs>
                        cunctisque ad se pertinentibus iuste et legaliter tam in <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, vallibus quamque in planiciebus
                        Ingelfredo glorioso comiti <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >iure proprietario</rs> concedimus et largimur, ac de nostro iure et
                        dominio in eius ius et dominium omnino transfundimus atque donamus ad
                        habensum, tenendum, vendendum, commutandum, alienandum, pro anima iudicandum
                        et quicquid voluerit faciendum absque totius potestatis contradicitone, si
                        quis igitur hoc nostrae auctoritatis et concessionis preceptum infringere
                        vel violare temptaverit, sciat se <rs key="#Penalty">compositurum auri
                            optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camerae
                            nostrae</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            predicto Ingelfredo</rs> glorioso comit[i s]uisque heredibus vel cui
                        ipse dederit aut habere concesserit. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius
                        observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter insigniri
                        iussimus. Signum domni (MF) Berengarii serenissimi imperatoris. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216"
                            >Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI n. III
                        framm.)</ab>
